  {
    "id": "ADULT-CARDIAC-001",
    "source": "MARUNTHAGAM_ADULT",
    "chief_complaint_pattern": "chest\\s*(pain|press(ure|ing)?|tight(ness)?|discomf(ort)?)|cardiac|மார்[பு][ிீு]?[ல்னை]*\\s*[஀-௿\\s]{0,30}?(வலி|இறுக்க|நெருக்கம்|பீடிப்)",
    "required_co_signals": [
      "(radiat|jaw|left\\s*arm|right\\s*arm|shoulder|தாடை|தோள்|பரவி|பரவ்|கழுத்தெலும்|கை[஀-௿]{0,3}\\s*(மரத்|வலி|மரத்துப்போ)|மரத்துப்போ)",
      "(dyspn|short(ness)?\\s*of\\s*breath|breathless|diaphor|cold\\s*sweat|tachycard|palpitat|heart\\s*racing|மூச்சு\\s*(திண|நெருக|இடை)|வியர்|பதற்ற|மரத்துப்போ|பரவி)"
    ],
    "negative_scoping": [],
    "age_group": "adolescent|adult|elderly",
    "duration_min_days": 0,
    "duration_max_days": null,
    "minimum_triage_level": "RED",
    "override_reason": "Cardiac-pattern symptoms (chest pain + radiation + autonomic/dyspnea). Same-day cardiology evaluation required REGARDLESS of patient self-attribution to anxiety/panic — symptom pattern alone is sufficient. v2.1 (2026-05-07): chief regex broadened to handle Tamil case-inflected forms of மார்பு (locative -இல், genitive -இன், accusative -ஐ, dative -க்கு) with up to 30 Tamil chars between the noun and the pain word. Co-signal also broadened to include `கை\\s*மரத்துப்போ` (arm numbness in compound form)."
  },
